    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Your special issue (May 7) provided a special gem, ''The Self-Discovery Dial,'' that indicates many of the innumerable facets of everyone's experience. Thank you for a vivid tool.</p>
        <p>J. Gordon Chamberlin  Greensboro, N.C.</p>
